My current issue: on my current branch 'nate-onboarding' which has previous commits / pushes and has some changes unstaged yet is a HUGE mess in terms of multiple different features being worked on. Essentially i want to seperate these features into 2 branches (either by creating 2 new branches to isolate these features and deleting this current branch or keep this current branch and remove one feature and add that other feature to a new branch). Here are the 2 features i'd like seperated: 1) the new onboarding flow and 2) the landing page and new doc system. Here's where things get complicated: 1) some previous commits have a mix of changes for both features, 2) some (but minimal) changes are used / shared by both features. Help me come up with a super specific plan to execute this! ultrathink 

Here's some context about my current branch, what fs should be isolated in its associated feature branch, and what potentially should be shared, and note that i may miss some things so ask me to clarify if i misses smth:

Specific changes / additions / deletions exclusively for the onboarding flow feature:
@src/components/vue/onboarding/ @src/components/composables/useOnboardingFlow.ts @src/stores/onboardingStore.ts @src/types/onboarding.ts @src/layouts/OnboardingLayout.astro @src/pages/onboarding.astro @src/constants/workflowRecommendations.ts @src/components/vue/modals/BaseModal.vue @src/components/vue/display/workflows/ 

Exclusively for landing page / docs feature / changes:
@src/components/vue/views/home/ @src/content/ @src/layouts/DocsLayout.astro @src/layouts/DashLayout.astro @src/layouts/Layout.astro @src/pages/docs/ @src/pages/index.astro @src/stores/docsStore.ts @src/components/vue/modals/DocsModal.vue @src/components/vue/docs/ @src/components/vue/display/Testimonial.vue @src/components/vue/buttons/LearnMoreButton.vue @src/components/vue/conductor/ 
@src/components/vue/ui/AiConductorGraphicV2.vue 

Ones I think i want in BOTH:
@src/components/vue/ui/AnimatedFloatingElement.vue @src/components/composables/useAnimateElement.ts @src/components/vue/ui/AnimatedCounter.vue @src/components/vue/ui/TutorialArrowInstance.vue @src/components/vue/ui/TutorialArrow.vue @src/components/vue/ui/FloatingElement.vue @src/components/vue/ui/TypewriterText.vue 

Ones im unsure about:
@src/components/composables/useAuth.ts @src/components/composables/useAnimationBus.ts 
@src/styles/typography.css @src/styles/design-system.css @src/styles/global.css @src/constants/animations.ts @astro.config.ts @package.json @pnpm-lock.yaml @tailwind.config.mjs  

Create a doc called SeperateBranchPlan.md with a proposed plan and startegy to do this. help me decide on the changes im unsure about. review my previous commits and tell me if im forgetting to account for anything. feel free to use gemini to review large files.

